number-is-nan

ES2015 Number.isNaN() ponyfill

Install

$ npm install --save number-is-nan

Usage

var numberIsNan = require('number-is-nan');

numberIsNan(NaN);
//=> true

numberIsNan('unicorn');
//=> false
